entries.title: Do you do Illustrations?
entries.description: As description UX/UI Developer I focus on the technical implementation of Designs. As a UX/UI Designer I focus on creating intuitive and apelaing designs. However, I do not create custom illustrations, fonts or do image editing - I leave that part to the talented creatives I work with.
